{"tid":2207655,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯領軍發動聯署推司法改革 藍營大狀都唔BUY","createTime":"2020-09-18T10:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:13:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79607ec2ea62d2bf96d64d9407ead556ea694585","tid":2207655,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"司法界最近俾左報同建制派連番狙擊，被批評放生「縱暴派」。藍營「大聲公」、本身為律師嘅立法會議員何君堯點會輸蝕？早前發起「KOL推動：改革司法制度，全民聯署」大行動。由何君堯領軍嘅活動，水平質素大家心中有數，就連建制派陣營嘅法律界都唔buy，7月時曾經報名參選新一屆立法會法律界選舉想挑戰郭榮鏗嘅麥慶歡大狀都好擔憂，主動出po話明「慎用政治運動方式推動司法改革」，話希望可以同何君堯理性討論。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係報名參選，麥慶歡都冇乜人識；雖然選舉押後咗，但似乎佢都仲好關注政圈動態，留意到何君堯又有舉動，似乎仍在積極備戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/OSCTXKPQWRATLEESILJBNKTLOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FOSCTXKPQWRATLEESILJBNKTLOM%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=65a43bc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FOSCTXKPQWRATLEESILJBNKTLOM%2F&h=aa011d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/OSCTXKPQWRATLEESILJBNKTLOM/</a>"},{"pid":"a5cd99850d494a91f8a76f2ca9da2115a94e2225","tid":2207655,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b6172307fe6c14df70f9a61a10df7b21f1c6e2","tid":2207655,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}